msgstr "Doctrina: Ofensiva"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/mission_option_select1"
msgid "Select your Doctrine for the mission:"
msgstr "Seleccione su Estrategia para la misión:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/name"
msgid "Escaping the Pocket"
msgstr "Escapando del Cerco"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/name_big"
msgid "Escaping the Pocket"
msgstr "Escapando del Cerco"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/01"
msgid ""
"Fallschirmjäger! We need to cross the river if we want to escape the Allied "
"encirclement. The river current makes it impossible to swim with all our "
"equipment attached."
msgstr ""
"¡Fallschirmjäger! Tenemos que cruzar el río si queremos escapar del cerco "
"aliado. La corriente del río hace imposible nadar con todo nuestro equipo a "
"cuestas."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/02"
msgid ""
"We have spread out into small squads to try to get through the Allied lines. "
"This sector has Americans at every corner, so watch out!"
msgstr ""
"Nos hemos dividido en pequeños escuadrones para intentar atravesar las "
"líneas aliadas. Este sector tiene americanos en cada esquina, así que ¡id "
"con cuidado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/03"
msgid ""
"Your first objective is to approach the bridge at Magny. We will see if it's "
"possible to cross the river at this point."
msgstr ""
"Tu primer objetivo es acercarte al puente de Magny. Veremos si es posible "
"cruzar el río en ese punto."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/04"
msgid ""
"It is up to you to either sneak through or blast your way through. But we "
"are at a severe disadvantage. So pick your fights very carefully."
msgstr ""
"Depende de usted ir en sigilo o abrirse paso a la fuerza. Pero estamos en "
"grave desventaja. Así que elige tus peleas con mucho cuidado."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/05"
msgid ""
"The shrubbery, the rain and the darkness make it very difficult to spot the "
"enemy. Move carefully and assume that wherever there may be lights, there "
"will be Americans."
msgstr ""
"Los arbustos, la lluvia y la oscuridad hacen que sea muy difícil detectar al "
"enemigo. Muévete con cuidado y asume que allí donde haya luces, habrá "
"americanos."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/06"
msgid ""
"This bridge is no good. It's barricaded and swarming with Americans. We also "
"risk them blowing it up if we get into a firefight. We need to find another "
"way!"
msgstr ""
"Este puente no nos sirve. Está atrincherado y lleno de americanos. También "
"corremos el riesgo de que lo vuelen si empezamos un tiroteo. ¡Necesitamos "
"encontrar otro camino!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/07"
msgid ""
"I hear gunshots! Kameraden, there is another squad being pinned down. Go and "
"assist them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oigo disparos! Kameraden, hay otro escuadrón siendo atacado. ¡Ve y ayúdales!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/08"
msgid ""
"Fallschirmjäger! It's good to see you. We bring bad news from Magny. The "
"bridge is a no-go. Have you found another way out?"
msgstr ""
"¡Fallschirmjäger! Me alegro de verle. Traemos malas noticias de Magny. El "
"puente es imposible de cruzar. ¿Han encontrado otra salida?"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/09"
msgid "And what is all that artillery gunfire?"
msgstr "¿Y qué son todos esos disparos de artillería?"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/10"
msgid ""
"... Hmm...  Some of us here speak french and english. I wonder if we could "
"convince the canadians to fire at their own allied positions by the river "
"ford..."
msgstr ""
"... Hmm...  Algunos de nosotros aquí hablamos francés e inglés. Me pregunto "
"si podríamos convencer a los canadienses a disparar contra sus propias "
"tropas cerca del vado del río ..."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/11"
msgid ""
"Excellent, we have a plan of attack! Go to that manor and get hold of an "
"American Radio back pack."
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente, tenemos un plan de ataque! Ve a esa mansión y hazte con una "
"mochila de Radio Americana."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/12"
msgid ""
"Excellent work. And there's all the maps laying around, too! Now, we shall "
"transmit the river ford coordinates."
msgstr ""
"Excelente. ¡Y también están todos los mapas de la zona! Ahora, "
"transmitiremos las coordenadas del vado del río."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/13"
msgid ""
"The artillery should have done its work. Fallschirmjäger! Cross the river by "
"the ford!"
msgstr ""
"La artillería debería haber hecho su trabajo. ¡Fallschirmjäger! ¡Crucen el "
"río por el vado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/14"
msgid ""
"Good job Fallschirmjäger! The last job for today is to fight your way to the "
"extraction point, let's go!"
msgstr ""
"¡Buen trabajo Fallschirmjäger! Solo queda abrirse camino hasta el punto de "
"extracción, ¡vamos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/15"
msgid ""
"Everybody, cross over to the north-east side of the river! The Allied forces "
"are arriving in large numbers to our previous positions!"
msgstr ""
"¡Todos, crucen al lado noreste del río! ¡Las fuerzas aliadas están llegando "
"en gran número por nuestra retaguardia!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator/wounded"
msgid ""
"I also see you have wounded soldiers! We will try to get you some medical "
"supplies!"
msgstr ""
"¡Veo que tienen soldados heridos! ¡Intentaremos conseguirles suministros "
"médicos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator2/01"
msgid ""
"Jawohl Herr Hauptmann! We located a ford in the river, but the Americans "
"spotted us and ruhed a whole damn armored column in to cover it."
msgstr ""
"¡Jawohl Herr Hauptmann! Localizamos un vado en el río, pero los americanos "
"nos vieron y enviaron toda una maldita columna blindada para cubrirlo."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator2/02"
msgid ""
"The Canadians and Americans want to prove whose artillery is more accurate. "
"They've been firing at multiple coordinates all evening."
msgstr ""
"Los canadienses y los americanos quieren demostrar quién tiene la artillería "
"más precisa. Llevan toda la tarde disparando en múltiples coordenadas."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/narrator2/03"
msgid ""
"We could definitely try, Herr Hauptmann! I believe the enemy is directing "
"the artillery from a radio station inside the nearby manor. "
msgstr ""
"¡Podríamos intentarlo, Herr Hauptmann! Creo que el enemigo está dirigiendo "
"la artillería desde una estación de radio dentro de una mansión cercana. "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Good work! This result would be called a victory if it wasn’t for the fact "
"we are retreating. But since you succeeded, we have a fighting chance to "
"keep the allies from breaking out in the direction of Paris. Well done!"
msgstr ""
"¡Buen trabajo! Este resultado se trataría de una victoria si no fuera por el "
"hecho de que nos estamos retirando. Pero tras este éxito, tenemos una "
"oportunidad de luchar para evitar que los aliados alcancen París. ¡Bien "
"hecho!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This is very bad news. We should have gotten out of this situation in order "
"to regroup, but largely due to this failed breakout we’re suddenly a lot "
"more likely to be taken prisoner, and that includes you! "
msgstr ""
"Estas son muy malas noticias. Deberíamos haber salido de esta situación para "
"reagruparnos, pero debido en gran parte a esta fuga fallida, tenemos muchas "
"más probabilidades de ser hechos prisioneros, ¡y eso te incluye a ti! "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/place"
msgid "3rd Fallschirmjäger Division "
msgstr "3ª División Fallschirmjäger "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/skip"
msgid "Skip preparation phase"
msgstr "Saltar la fase de preparación"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/story"
msgid " August 1944. The German counterattack at Mortain has failed to achieve its goals, and the allies are breaking out of the bridgehead. The threat of encirclement is real; but even now, Hitler demands new counter attacks in the direction of Avranches. A few days later he finally approves a retreat east. But around Falaise the remnants of no less than 14 divisions, including yours, are being pushed back into a pocket, and the few roads east from Falaise are constantly under attack by allied aircraft and artillery. High command has ordered a breakout by night.\n\n In this mission, the plan for you and the 3rd Fallschirmjäger Division is to break out of the encirclement in small groups. You will command one group, and you are to infiltrate and push through the allied lines, while creating some big distractions to get their attention. Your first assignment is to find a way for the division to cross the river Dives. Once you have found a suitable place to cross, report to 3rd FJ division command, after which further instructions will be issued.\n\nGood luck!"
msgstr ""
"Agosto, 1944.\n"
"\n"
"El contraataque alemán en Mortain no ha logrado\n"
"\n"
"alcanzar sus objetivos, y los aliados están rompiendo la\n"
"\n"
"cabeza de playa. La amenaza de un cerco es real; pero incluso\n"
"\n"
"en esta situación, Hitler exige nuevos contraataques en dirección a\n"
"\n"
"Avranches. Unos días más tarde, finalmente aprueba una retirada\n"
"\n"
"hacia el este. Pero alrededor de Falaise los restos de no menos de\n"
"\n"
"14 divisiones, incluyendo la suya, están siendo conducidos de nuevo hacia\n"
"\n"
"un cerco, y las pocas carreteras al este de Falaise son constantemente\n"
"\n"
"atacadas por la aviación aliada y la artillería.\n"
"\n"
"El alto mando ha ordenado una fuga nocturna.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"En esta misión, el plan para usted y la 3ª División Fallschirmjäger\n"
"\n"
"es romper el cerco en pequeños grupos.\n"
"\n"
"Usted comandará un grupo, y debe infiltrarse\n"
"\n"
"y avanzar a través de las líneas aliadas, mientras idean\n"
"\n"
"algunas distracciones que puedan llamar su atención.\n"
"\n"
"Su primera tarea es encontrar una forma de que la\n"
"\n"
"División cruce el río Dives.\n"
"\n"
"Una vez que haya encontrado un lugar adecuado para cruzar, informe al\n"
"\n"
"mando de la 3ª división FJ, después espere\n"
"\n"
"instrucciones adicionales.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"¡Buena suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/task1"
msgid "Approach the Magny bridge to perform reconnaissance."
msgstr "Acercarse al puente de Magny para realizar un reconocimiento."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/task2"
msgid "Rescue the friendly squad."
msgstr "Rescatar al escuadrón aliado."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/task3"
msgid ""
"Acquire an American portable radio to give false artillery coordinates in "
"order to eliminate the US forces at the ford."
msgstr ""
"Adquirir una radio portátil estadounidense para dar falsas coordenadas de "
"artillería con el fin de eliminar a las fuerzas estadounidenses en el vado."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/task4"
msgid "Cross the river by the fording area."
msgstr "Cruzar el río por la zona del vado."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/task5"
msgid "Escape the falaise pocket by fighting your way to the extraction point."
msgstr ""
"Escapar del cerco de falaise luchando hasta llegar al punto de extracción."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_19_falaise_escape/taskopt1"
msgid "Bring medical supplies to the wounded soldiers."
msgstr "Llevar suministros médicos a los soldados heridos."
